cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a system for classification of breast specimens based on convolutional neural networks, which is a common approach in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). The focus of the system is on the assessment of tumor-associated stroma, which is a specific aspect of histopathology images and could also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
